com.gluonhq.charm.glisten.visual

Enum Swatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Swatch>
      • com.gluonhq.charm.glisten.visual.Swatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Swatch>

    public enum Swatch
extends java.lang.Enum<Swatch>
    An enumeration of all available swatch styles provided by Glisten. A swatch is simply a color scheme that can be applied to Glisten applications. The default swatch is blue.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Theme
